           <h2 class="show_sub_title"><a target="_blank" href="https://amzn.to/2JkwPn6">3. Ring Video Doorbell Pro</a></h2>
           <p>With a motion-activated camera, two-way audio and brilliant HD video, you’ll never miss a visitor again. See, hear and speak to whoever is at your door in real time from your smartphone, tablet or desktop. Day or night, rain or shine—you’re always home.</p>
           <a target="_blank" href="https://amzn.to/2JkwPn6"><img src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-d_C7KpO9KxQ/Wh-pBftW67I/AAAAAAAAB30/3oXA_dsvRcoedLpepkIs4eJl3SrqkEmvwCLcBGAs/s1600/ring.gif"></a>
           <h5>via Amazon.com</h5>
           <p class="show_p">With four interchangeable faceplates included in your purchase, you can select a finish that fits your style. Choose between Satin Black, Venetian, Satin Nickel and Pearl White to customize your doorbell to match your home.</p>
           <button><a target="_blank" href="https://amzn.to/2JkwPn6">Learn More</a></button>
