           <p class="show_p">Evapolar is a personal air cooler that allows you to create your own micro climate. Evapolar is a 3 in 1 device: it cools, humidifies, and cleans the dust particles from the air making it healthier for you. It doesn't take much time or effort to install Evapolar – just pour water in the tank, plug it in and enjoy. This smart new solution for the cooling market provides a device that actually cools the air,using the size and power consumption of a small fan.</p>
